#. type: Title =
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Enable Basic authentication"
msgstr "启用基本认证"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Enable Basic authentication for your Quarkus project and allow users to "
"authenticate with a username and password."
msgstr "为你的Quarkus项目启用基本认证，允许用户用用户名和密码进行认证。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "先决条件"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You have installed at least one extension that provides an "
"`IdentityProvider` based on username and password, such as xref:security-"
"jdbc.adoc[Elytron JDBC]."
msgstr ""
"您至少安装了一个根据用户名和密码提供 `IdentityProvider` 的扩展，如 xref:security-jdbc.adoc[Elytron "
"JDBC] 。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure"
msgstr "程序"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Enable Basic authentication by setting the value of `quarkus.http.auth."
"basic` property to `true`."
msgstr "通过将 `quarkus.http.auth.basic` 属性的值设置为 `true` ，启用 Basic 身份验证。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"An easy way to configure the required user credentials for Basic "
"authentication to work is to configure the user name, secret, and roles "
"directly in the `application.properties` file."
msgstr "配置基本身份验证所需的用户凭证的简单方法是直接在 `application.properties` 文件中配置用户名、密 码和角色。"

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Example of Basic authentication properties"
msgstr "基本身份验证属性示例"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In this configuration the credentials for users `alice` and `bob` are "
"configured: `alice` has a password `alice` and an `admin` role, `bob` has a "
"password `bob` and a `user` role."
msgstr ""
"在此配置中，为用户 `alice` 和 `bob` 配置了凭据： `alice` 有一个密码 `alice` 和一个 `admin` 角色， `bob` "
"有一个密码 `bob` 和一个 `user` 角色。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"For more information, see xref:security-testing.adoc#configuring-user-"
"information[Configuring User Information] in the \"Security Testing\" guide."
msgstr ""
"更多信息，请参阅 \"安全测试 \"指南中的 xref:security-testing.adoc#configuring-user-"
"information[配置用户信息] 。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Configuring user names, secrets, and roles in the `application.properties` "
"file is only suitable for testing scenarios. If you are securing an "
"application for production, always use a database to store this information."
msgstr ""
"在 `application.properties` "
"文件中配置用户名、机密和角色只适用于测试场景。如果要确保生产应用程序的安全，请务必使用数据库来存储这些信息。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.16/guides/security-basic-authentication-howto.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To walk through how to configure Basic authentication together with JPA for "
"storing user credentials in a database, see the xref:security-basic-"
"authentication-tutorial.adoc[Secure a Quarkus application with Basic "
"authentication] tutorial."
msgstr ""
"要了解如何将 Basic 身份验证与 JPA 一起配置，以便在数据库中存储用户凭证，请参阅 xref:security-basic-"
"authentication-tutorial.adoc[使用 Basic 身份验证确保 Quarkus 应用程序安全] 教程。"

